		a[j]++;

	  }

	for(j=0; j<lose.size(); j++){

		win = true;
		break;
	  }
	}
	if(!win){
	  lose.push_back(i);
	  ans[i]=1;
	}
  }
/*  for(i=0; i<lose.size(); i++)
